org.fcrepo.kernel.modeshape.observer

Class FedoraEventImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.kernel.modeshape.observer.FedoraEventImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.fcrepo.kernel.api.observer.FedoraEvent

    public class FedoraEventImpl
extends Object
implements org.fcrepo.kernel.api.observer.FedoraEvent
    A very simple abstraction to prevent event-driven machinery downstream from the repository from relying directly on a JCR interface Event. Can represent either a single JCR event or several.
    Since:
    Feb 19, 2013
    Author:
    ajs6f
